ID: Changes to this doc can break the nose tests or interfere with test systems!  BEFORE making changes, please read https://confluence.oceanobservatories.org/display/CIDev/Preload+development.  AFTER making changes, please TEST, make a copy of this sheet, and commit the new URL to ion_loader.py!

unused/start_agent: only base node in topology should start
platform_id: if using the simulator, this MUST be a value defined in the simulator configuration network.yml
agent_device_map: don't need -- already have platform_device_id in colF for each platform_id
agent_streamconfig_map: define from streamdef and parameter dictionary L360
alerts: references a list of Alerts sheet ids
publish_rate: publishing rate (aparam_pubrate_config) for the agent, zero means publish every granule as it arrives
